title: Obama focusing on condolences, not gun laws, in Oregon visit
text: > Top News Obama focusing on condolences, not gun laws, in Oregon visit Demonstrators wait outside of Roseburg Regional Airport for President Barack Obama's arrival in Roseburg, Ore., Friday, Oct. 9, 2015. More than 200 gun-rights activists protested Obama’s visit on Friday to Oregon to meet with the families of victims of last week’s campus killings. The protesters were angry about Obama’s calls for gun restrictions in the wake of the shooting rampage that killed eight students and a teacher at Umpqua Community College. (AP Photo/Ryan Kang)
